tion, Army Research Lab, Army Research Office, National Institute of Standards and Technology and an industry grant. She is UIC’s principal investigator (PI) for four of these five awards. Each grant is for a different research project, but they all have a common thread – Edge computing. Edge computing is about extending the frontier of computing applications, data, and services away from centralized nodes to the logical&hellip;</div> <a class="read_more" href="https://www.ece.uic.edu/2018/10/31/taking-research-to-the-edge/" title="More... Taking Research to the ‘Edge’">More...</a></article></div></div><div class="masonry-item"><div class="inner content-wrap k2t-element-hover"><div class="post-img attachment-thumb_150x150 size-thumb_150x150 wp-post-image"> <a href="https://www.ece.uic.edu/2018/09/25/new-engineering-organization-building-electric-car-and-opportunities/"><img width="150" height="150" src="https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Formula-One-Race-Car-drawing_WEB-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail" alt="UIC engineering VESE race car" size="thumbnail" return="" srcset="https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Formula-One-Race-Car-drawing_WEB-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Formula-One-Race-Car-drawing_WEB-55x55.jpg 55w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Formula-One-Race-Car-drawing_WEB-80x80.jpg 80w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Formula-One-Race-Car-drawing_WEB-130x130.jpg 130w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Formula-One-Race-Car-drawing_WEB-100x100.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /></a></div><article class="news-article wrapper"> <span class="news-title"><a class="post_title w4pl_post_title" href="https://www.ece.uic.edu/2018/09/25/new-engineering-organization-building-electric-car-and-opportunities/" title="View New Engineering Organization Building Electric Car and Opportunities">New Engineering Organization Building Electric Car and Opportunities</a></span> <span class="post-date">September 25, 2018</span><div class="post-excerpt">Tesla has the Model S, Nissan offers the Leaf, and Chevy makes the Bolt. Soon, UIC will have an electric car, too. A new student organization in the College of Engineering called Vehicle Electronics and System Engineering (VESE) is engineering’s newest organization offering students an opportunity to be pioneers as they start designing and building a formula one electric race car to compete in an SAE sanctioned competition next semester in Lincoln, Nebraska, in May. “The beauty of our car is that it is based on electrical systems, but there are mechanical components that have to be built like any other race car,” said Amru Qutub, a student in the Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering (ECE) and the president&hellip;</div> <a class="read_more" href="https://www.ece.uic.edu/2018/09/25/new-engineering-organization-building-electric-car-and-opportunities/" title="More... New Engineering Organization Building Electric Car and Opportunities">More...</a></article></div></div><div class="masonry-item"><div class="inner content-wrap k2t-element-hover"><div class="post-img attachment-thumb_150x150 size-thumb_150x150 wp-post-image"> <a href="https://www.ece.uic.edu/2018/09/06/the-new-york-times-references-professor-lins-research/"><img width="150" height="150" src="https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/lin-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail" alt="Image of Prof. James Lin" size="thumbnail" return="" srcset="https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/lin-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/lin-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/lin-55x55.jpg 55w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/lin-80x80.jpg 80w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/lin-130x130.jpg 130w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/upload